{"id": "1456546547063062659", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "818119680073793547", "author_name": ".losya", "author_bot": false, "content": "サルバドル、序盤から強すぎておすすめです\nメイン垢でストーリークリアできなくて泣いた所をサブ垢はおじじ一人でサクサク行くので…", "timestamp": "2026-01-02T07:15:58.146000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1456552659015172118", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "957714658872164412", "author_name": "shiromishi_low", "author_bot": false, "content": "混沌の狭間に行きたいのですが、どんな編成にすればいいのでしょうか？混沌のキャラ性能をあんまり知らなくて……\n初心者なのもあって混沌属性の限定キャラは一人もいません……恒常はパンディア以外いると思います\n普段は超次元を主に使ってます、ここでおすすめしてもらったタイスとサルバドルとダフォダイルは頑張って取りました", "timestamp": "2026-01-02T07:40:15.349000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1456553727300206698", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "これのことですかね？", "timestamp": "2026-01-02T07:44:30.048000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1456553726927044608", "filename": "Screenshot_20260102-164414.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2162584, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1456553726927044608/Screenshot_20260102-164414.png?ex=6a344a9d&is=6a32f91d&hm=050125a6265365b363d9d7aa2c8a31aa20d4f50a495b13498bc049ce87ed7f75&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
